# Reader v2 uses the same env merge as the main app: monorepo root `.env` / `.env.local`
# are applied first via `env-bootstrap.ts` (see root `.env.example` for the full list).
#
# Copy the root `.env.example` to the repo root as `.env` and set at least:
# - PAYLOAD_SECRET
# - DATABASE_URL (+ PAYLOAD_DB_PROVIDER)
# - Clerk keys if you use Clerk (optional for Payload-only dev)
#
# Optional: link back to the main portfolio site from the reader shell.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MAIN_SITE_URL=https://example.com
